## About the template

We must pay respects to indexhibit.org, who are most directly responsible for the layout of this template. A few other references:

- [Cargo](https://f934.cargo.site/Aenean-Facili)
- [Sabine Rovers' website](https://sabinerovers.com/Au-Maroc)
- [I like this layout](https://davidroethlisberger.ch/Projekte)
- [I like the layout here on the sidebar?](http://www.ricardoloureiro.com/)

